%% Search lifecycle for the merge service.
%% Reference: download-proxy/src/merge_service/search.py:270 SearchOrchestrator.search().
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant FE as Frontend (Angular :4200 / :7187)
    participant API as FastAPI /api/v1/search (:7187)
    participant ORCH as SearchOrchestrator
    participant T1 as Tracker 1..N (subprocess nova3)
    participant T2 as Private Tracker (aiohttp)
    participant DEDUP as Deduplicator
    participant ENRICH as MetadataEnricher
    participant SSE as /api/v1/search/stream

    User->>FE: enters query
    FE->>API: POST /api/v1/search { query, category, sort_by, ... }
    API->>ORCH: search(query, category)
    ORCH->>ORCH: create SearchMetadata(search_id=uuid)

    par fan-out (asyncio.gather, no semaphore today)
        ORCH->>T1: subprocess python3 -c <engine>.search()
        T1-->>ORCH: stdout JSON list of SearchResult dicts
    and
        ORCH->>T2: aiohttp POST login + GET search (rutracker/kinozal/nnmclub/iptorrents)
        T2-->>ORCH: HTML → parsed SearchResult list
    end

    ORCH->>ORCH: store _tracker_results[search_id][name]
    User->>FE: opens SSE stream
    FE->>SSE: GET /api/v1/search/stream/{search_id}
    SSE->>ORCH: get_live_results(search_id)
    ORCH-->>SSE: incremental SearchResult list
    SSE-->>FE: data: {...} (per result, deduped by seen_hashes)

    ORCH->>DEDUP: merge_results(all_results)
    DEDUP-->>ORCH: List[MergedResult]
    opt enable_metadata
        ORCH->>ENRICH: fill best_quality + CanonicalIdentity fields
        ENRICH-->>ORCH: enriched MergedResult list
    end
    ORCH-->>API: SearchMetadata(status="completed", merged_results=N)
    API-->>FE: SearchResponse JSON
    FE-->>User: renders sorted, deduped, freeleech-aware results
